{
  "stem": "17526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 92.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But as time went on, they have given out edicts that the whole town has to come-- this was in late, I guess, 1942, when they already were well-established.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They already have conquered all of Poland and they were surging into Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then they were trying to deal with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In 1942-- --it was in the spring of '42, they have organized this big selection.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was called the punkt-- the punkt means point-- where they have summoned all the-- by summoned, they have-- they have made plenty clear that everybody that is not going to report-- all the Jews, that are not going to report on this date to this place are going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Of course, there were some heroes who tried to do it and they were shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Imagine thousands of people, a whole town, being ordered into one big football field, which was at the outskirts of the town.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was the Jewish football field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that selection took about three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was absolutely an unforgettable experience and just talking about it makes me freeze.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were thousands of people, naturally our family and everybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in the morning, it was a sunny spring day, I remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the sun was shining.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And as we walked, from all the streets, all these roads led to one main street leading to this football field.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was just a sight I had never seen before-- thousands of kids, old people, sick people, lame and blind people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "All the people were streaming to this here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then the whole place was surrounded by Nazis with machine gun-- guns and dogs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And at one point, one center on this football field, there were these Nazis and there was this famous selection, the first one.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
